**Haftalik Laravel Deployment Rejasi**

## **1-kun (Git - Asoslar va Ishlash jarayoni)**  
**‚è≥ 5 soat*

### **Git branchlar va ishlash jarayoni (2 soat)**
- `git init`, `git clone`, `git branch`, `git checkout`, `git switch`
- `git merge` va `git rebase` farqlari

### **Pull Request va Code Review (2 soat)**
- GitHub, GitLab yoki Bitbucket'da PR yaratish
- Konfliktlarni hal qilish

### **Amaliy mashg‚Äòulot (1 soat)**
- O‚Äòz loyihangda branch yaratish, kod qo‚Äòshish, PR ochish, merge qilish

---

## **2-kun (CI/CD - GitHub Actions)**  
**‚è≥ 5 soat**

### **CI/CD asoslari (1 soat)**
- Continuous Integration va Continuous Deployment tushunchalari

### **GitHub Actions (2 soat)**
- YAML formatida workflow yaratish
- Laravel uchun CI/CD setup qilish

### **Amaliy mashg‚Äòulot (2 soat)**
- Laravel loyihang uchun GitHub Actions bilan avtomatlashtirish

---

## **3-kun (Jenkins va Laravel Forge)**  
**‚è≥ 5 soat**

### **Jenkins asoslari (2 soat)**
- Jenkins o‚Äòrnatish va konfiguratsiya
- Laravel loyihasi uchun build pipeline yaratish

### **Laravel Forge bilan deployment (2 soat)**
- Forge orqali server yaratish va deploy qilish

### **Amaliy mashg‚Äòulot (1 soat)**
- O‚Äòz loyihangni Jenkins yoki Laravel Forge orqali deploy qilish

---

## **4-kun (Envoy & Laravel Deployment)**  
**‚è≥ 5 soat**

### **Laravel Envoy (2 soat)**
- Envoy skript yozish
- Deployment jarayonini avtomatlashtirish

### **Deployment usullari (Nginx & Apache) (2 soat)**
- Laravelni Nginx va Apache serverlariga joylash

### **Amaliy mashg‚Äòulot (1 soat)**
- Laravel loyihangni Envoy orqali deploy qilish

---

## **5-kun (Supervisor va PM2 bilan Laravel Background Jobs)**  
**‚è≥ 5 soat**

### **Supervisor (2 soat)**
- Laravel queue ishini avtomatlashtirish

### **PM2 (Node.js uchun) (2 soat)**
- Laravel websockets va queue monitoring

### **Amaliy mashg‚Äòulot (1 soat)**
- Supervisor yoki PM2 orqali Laravel workerlarni boshqarish

---

## **6-kun (Amaliy Deployment va Troubleshooting)**  
**‚è≥ 5 soat**

### **Deployment testlari (2 soat)**
- GitHub Actions yoki Jenkins orqali avtomatik testlar

### **Laravel production muhitini optimallashtirish (2 soat)**
- `.env` sozlamalari, `php artisan config:cache` va `route:cache`

### **Amaliy mashg‚Äòulot (1 soat)**
- Laravel loyihangni serverga joylash va test qilish

---

## **7-kun (Qayta ko‚Äòrib chiqish va yakuniy loyiha)**  
**‚è≥ 5 soat**

### **O‚Äòtgan mavzularni takrorlash (2 soat)**

### **Amaliy loyiha deployment (3 soat)**
- Laravel loyihangni GitHub Actions yoki Jenkins orqali serverga deploy qilish

---

Ushbu reja asosida ishlasang, hafta oxirida Laravel loyihangni Git, CI/CD, Supervisor va PM2 bilan avtomatik deploy qilishni o‚Äòrganib olasan! üöÄ

